  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Take Control</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take control of a high-speed commuter train and master the tight schedule. Your passengers are counting on you, but watch out for unexpected threats that could derail your plans! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/882250/extras/21904553b6e078464e147e101e49300f.poster.avif?t=1755986553\" width=616 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/882250/extras/21904553b6e078464e147e101e49300f.webm?t=1755986553\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/882250/extras/21904553b6e078464e147e101e49300f.mp4?t=1755986553\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Make a Living</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Need some extra cash? Take on side gigs by helping locals, competing in the arena, or diving into the city’s underground scene. When the workday ends, relax at hotspots like the club, arcade, or casino. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/882250/extras/22b22d68ae1aadc5af42e8f4d918111a.poster.avif?t=1755986553\" width=616 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/882250/extras/22b22d68ae1aadc5af42e8f4d918111a.webm?t=1755986553\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/882250/extras/22b22d68ae1aadc5af42e8f4d918111a.mp4?t=1755986553\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Drop Some Cash</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the city’s shops and choose from a wide variety of items. Stock up on food and drinks, furnish and decorate your home, or find new outfits to express your style. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/882250/extras/9fd1f134c72fd207a2b848a888d196d9.avif?t=1755986553\" width=616 height=212 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Make Your Mark</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your living situation by moving into a new home and personalizing it with furniture, decorations, and paint. Not ready for a big move? Lay low at the local hotel until the time is right. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/882250/extras/7b13d53205ec5c4f98a621267fa293ee.poster.avif?t=1755986553\" width=616 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/882250/extras/7b13d53205ec5c4f98a621267fa293ee.webm?t=1755986553\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/882250/extras/7b13d53205ec5c4f98a621267fa293ee.mp4?t=1755986553\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Stay in Touch</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your smartphone is your lifeline in the city. Manage your properties, order pizza, check your messages, and set your alarm. Just don’t forget to pay your bills—life doesn’t stop, even in the fast lane! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/882250/extras/abfdf0dd04aca863b52243eead3230ff.avif?t=1755986553\" width=616 height=310 /></span></h2>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Take Control</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take control of a high-speed commuter train and master the tight schedule. Your passengers are counting on you, but watch out for unexpected threats that could derail your plans! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/882250/extras/21904553b6e078464e147e101e49300f.poster.avif?t=1755986553\" width=616 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/882250/extras/21904553b6e078464e147e101e49300f.webm?t=1755986553\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/882250/extras/21904553b6e078464e147e101e49300f.mp4?t=1755986553\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Make a Living</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Need some extra cash? Take on side gigs by helping locals, competing in the arena, or diving into the city’s underground scene. When the workday ends, relax at hotspots like the club, arcade, or casino. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/882250/extras/22b22d68ae1aadc5af42e8f4d918111a.poster.avif?t=1755986553\" width=616 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/882250/extras/22b22d68ae1aadc5af42e8f4d918111a.webm?t=1755986553\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/882250/extras/22b22d68ae1aadc5af42e8f4d918111a.mp4?t=1755986553\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Drop Some Cash</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the city’s shops and choose from a wide variety of items. Stock up on food and drinks, furnish and decorate your home, or find new outfits to express your style. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/882250/extras/9fd1f134c72fd207a2b848a888d196d9.avif?t=1755986553\" width=616 height=212 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Make Your Mark</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your living situation by moving into a new home and personalizing it with furniture, decorations, and paint. Not ready for a big move? Lay low at the local hotel until the time is right. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/882250/extras/7b13d53205ec5c4f98a621267fa293ee.poster.avif?t=1755986553\" width=616 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/882250/extras/7b13d53205ec5c4f98a621267fa293ee.webm?t=1755986553\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/882250/extras/7b13d53205ec5c4f98a621267fa293ee.mp4?t=1755986553\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Stay in Touch</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your smartphone is your lifeline in the city. Manage your properties, order pizza, check your messages, and set your alarm. Just don’t forget to pay your bills—life doesn’t stop, even in the fast lane! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/882250/extras/abfdf0dd04aca863b52243eead3230ff.avif?t=1755986553\" width=616 height=310 /></span></h2>",
